As far as the movies, they are very good. Highly recommended.

Bought this as a gift for my daughter's birthday.  We are huge fans of Tim Burton and only really wanted Sweeney Todd.  Sleepy Hollow was a bonus, and not unwelcome, but we could not find just Sweeney Todd alone.  Everything worked as expected, and movie was great, of course.  One note, beware if you are squeamish, Sweeney Todd is extremely violent and bloody.  Not for the uninitiated.
Love anything Johnny Depp!

Sleepy Hollow is a very clever adaptation of this tale, and Johnny Depp brings it off very well. It ranks well among terror movies. Sweeney Todd isn't as successful. It is a musical. I've seen better productions of this detailing the horror of the barber.
two great movies for a great price, very happy with purchase!
